Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}蛤？哦，不，不。我还活着\N{\fnArial\fs48}What? Oh, no no. I'm alive.
