Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:55.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是刚才的我们\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah. It's us from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对，我正试着\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, I was just trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}用脑子搞清楚融合舞呢\N{\fnArial\fs48}get my head around this fusion dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:02.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}融合舞和脑子没关系！\N{\fnArial\fs48}A fusion dance ain't about your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，你们是宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait, you guys are gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们一定要帮帮我啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}You've got to help me out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我想要和罗丝融合\N{\fnArial\fs48}I need to be able to fuse with Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}首先，你需要有一个宝石作为存在的基础\N{\fnArial\fs48}First, you need the gem at the core of your being.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}然后，你需要一个能变成光的身体\N{\fnArial\fs48}Then you need the body that could turn into light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}之后，你需要一个你能信任的变成光的同伴\N{\fnArial\fs48}Then you need the partner who you trust with that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是比喻？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Metaphorically?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并不\N{\fnArial\fs48}Literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:23.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘘。别啊，我还想看他试试\N{\fnArial\fs48}Shh. Come on. I still want to see him try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:26.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，珍珠是对的。我完全做不到\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh, so it's true. I really can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:28.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我简直在跟自己开玩笑\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm kidding myself with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我永远也不可能变成宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm never gonna be a gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:34.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，给我们点私密空间\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, give us some privacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我告诉你点秘密，宇宙先生\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let me tell you something, Mr. Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我觉得你能做到\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}I{\i} think you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但像珍珠那样跳舞并没有用\N{\fnArial\fs48}But it won't work if you dance like Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你要跳出自己的风格\N{\fnArial\fs48}You have to dance like {\i1}you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你要有自己的融合的方式\N{\fnArial\fs48}You have to fuse your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}做到开放、坦诚\N{\fnArial\fs48}Get open. Get honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:52.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}坚持自我。这就是融合\N{\fnArial\fs48}Invent yourselves together. That's fusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:54.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}眼...猜我了解了。\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Eye...{\i} {\i1}Think I get it.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.00,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,80)}此处舞蹈与布景致敬少女革命：绝对命运默示录
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们-我们没融合\N{\fnArial\fs48}We -- we didn't fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你肯定不能融合\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can't fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是人类\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:51.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道！这就是问题！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know! That's the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只是个人类\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm just a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:55.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这不是问题。我爱人类\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's not a problem. I love humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们都那么有趣\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're all so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}听着，过去几个月非常美好——哦，是的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look, these last few months have been great. Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:04.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我开始对将来有些担心\N{\fnArial\fs48}But I'm getting a little worried about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，那问问石榴\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, just ask Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:09.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我开始怀疑你是否...在乎我？\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm starting to wonder if you...Respect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:15.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，你真幽默，宇宙先生\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, you're hilarious, Mr. Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}罗丝，求求你\N{\fnArial\fs48}Rose, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:19.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你能不能\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:23.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}和我说人话，哪怕是一秒？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Talk to me for one second like a real person?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:30.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我...不是人类\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm {\i1}not{\i}a real person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我以为-我们难道还没-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I thought -- haven't we --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}难道不该这样吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}is this not how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:38.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，天哪\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这太诡异了。你真是个外星人\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is so weird. You really are an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你为什么笑了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你怎么又哭了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:53.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们该怎么办？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How are we gonna make this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:54.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}融合？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Fusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，是我们的关系\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:59.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们真的，非常不同\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're really, really different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们现在该怎么办？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:06.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们先...聊聊吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's just...Talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我根本不了解你\N{\fnArial\fs48}I barely know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:08.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是个好事\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们的关系进展的真有点快了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We really rushed into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}地球上的一切对我来讲都太快了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Everything on earth seems fast to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:16.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你想念你的母星吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Do you miss your home planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，从不\N{\fnArial\fs48}No. Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:21.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你最后是怎么和，呃，，走到一起的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How did you end up with, uh, Harpo, Groucho, and chico?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.05,0:09:21.32,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,275)}Harpo,Groucho和Chico是Marx Brothers（马克斯兄弟）的成员。Marx Brothers是美国喜剧界早期著名团体，与卓别林，劳埃德齐名，擅长无政府主义风格。\NHarpo对应石榴（沉默寡言），Groucho对应紫晶（直率），\NChico（经常有夸张行为）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:23.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？哦，她们\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh? Oh, them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们三个的故事可长了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Those are three long stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他们在干吗？——嘘！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are they doing? Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你喜欢过其他人类吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Have you loved other humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有——有\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:37.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那你，爱过，人类吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Have you ever been {\i1}in{\i} love with a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我怎么知道？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是一种折磨\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}格雷格\N{\fnArial\fs48}Greg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}罗丝\N{\fnArial\fs48}Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是折磨吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is this torture?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}最可怕的那种\N{\fnArial\fs48}The worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我实在对不起\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？不，不用\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh? No. Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:55.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?! Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:57.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，我太困惑了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我也是\N{\fnArial\fs48}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，呃，这不错\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, uh, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们总算有一个共同点了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We've got one thing in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha!Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他们还在跳舞？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why are they still dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那-那-那根本行不通啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I-it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，他们成了。——啊？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, it did. What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:12.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}已经成功了\N{\fnArial\fs48}It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:15.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我觉得这是我最喜欢的人类\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think this one's my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:19.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我觉得他也是她最喜欢的人了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think he's {\i1}her{\i} favorite, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:25.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，你们一直都不能融合？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, you guys were never able to fuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，不能\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:29.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但那不如与对方沟通重要\N{\fnArial\fs48}But that wasn't as important as talking to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}听着，人类和宝石人——\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look, humans and gems --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这仍是一个未知的领域\N{\fnArial\fs48}it's still some pretty new territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们需要共同探索\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're gonna have to work it out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且，康妮，如果你需要\N{\fnArial\fs48}And, Connie, if you ever need to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}向另一个人类谈论此事\N{\fnArial\fs48}to another human being about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:41.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你永远可以找我\N{\fnArial\fs48}you can always talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:42.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm.
